371
00:20:02,950 --> 00:20:03,580
Di sana.

372
00:20:14,070 --> 00:20:14,980
Hati-hati.

373
00:20:15,520 --> 00:20:17,440
Ia tidak wajar karena terus kabur.

374
00:20:17,710 --> 00:20:18,610
Mungkin ia takut.

375
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,100
